只有你一個。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好掛住我既小狗，幾日前離開左我，希望佢係天家會開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考慮左好撚多年啦😓"},{"pid":"224ba7ed2f7f0a963b84a286342cac04fdd40066","tid":329741,"uid":113429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:04:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83bfdfa6c7e3ef7411580588e81f4d90bae84b68","tid":329741,"uid":73730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過如果樓主真係長時間成日唔係屋企 經常要出差<br />\n咁似乎對狗仔都唔太好</blockquote><br />\n其實同屋企人同住<br />\n諗緊點說服佢地</blockquote><br />\n你要諗下屋企人肯唔肯幫手湊<br />\n如果你咁既情況 其實咪即話屋企人湊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83ad8fedf0d47a1ed3ce401ca80e4962b5ca8fb","tid":329741,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過如果樓主真係長時間成日唔係屋企 經常要出差<br />\n咁似乎對狗仔都唔太好</blockquote><br />\n其實同屋企人同住<br />\n諗緊點說服佢地</blockquote><br />\n你要諗下屋企人肯唔肯幫手湊<br />\n如果你咁既情況 其實咪即話屋企人湊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我想養左n年都唔敢養<br />\n驚累撚左隻狗"},{"pid":"fba5ffb1f4f0c55ae58c842a9d980f4465d4a884","tid":329741,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"心絲蟲果到就打針啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一年打一枝或者食藥就一個月一次遲咗好麻煩"}]}